data.title: Sultanate of Malacca – Numista
data.meta_description: Detailed information about the coin 1 Pitis, Muzaffar Shah, Sultanate of Malacca, with pictures and collection and swap management: mintage, descriptions, metal, weight, size, value and other numismatic data
data.text:
Obverse

Arabic inscription in two lines.

Script: Arabic

Lettering:

مظفر شاه

السلطان

Unabridged legend: muẓaffar syah al-sulṭan

Translation: The Sultan Muzaffar Shah

Reverse

Interlaced Arabic inscription.

Script: Arabic

Lettering: ناصر الدنيا والدين

Unabridged legend: naṣir al-dunya wa ad-din.

Translation: Helper of the World and Religion (of Islam)

Edge

Plain
